*mozc-2.17.2123.102 (21 Sep 2015)

  21 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> metadata.xml, +mozc-2.17.2123.102.ebuild:
  Add version 2.17.2123.102.

   GYP_DEFINES="use_libzinnia=0" became a default behavior in upstream.
  Installing app-i18n/zinnia to system-global isn't necessary.
   (But using app-i18n/zinnia-tomoe instead of app-i18n/tegaki-zinnia-
  japanese,
  app-i18n/zinnia-tomoe is depends on app-i18n/zinnia.)

   Now upstream goes Git fully, all submodules are cloned and checked out.
  It reduces deps, build time will be slower but simple.

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> mozc-2.17.2097.102.ebuild:
  Update ebuild file format from "# $Header: $" to "# $Id"

   Since Gentoo changes the VCS from CVS to git, ebuild header is changed.

